# fa19-516-162: Cloudmesh Shell

## E.Cloudmesh.Shell.2: Write a new command with your firstname as the command name.

### Steps

1. Go to directory where virtual environment was created

    ``cd cm``
    
2. Activate virtual environment

    ``ENV3\Scripts\activate.bat``

3. Create new command

    ``cms sys command generate katukota``

4. Check if command added
    
    ``cms help``
    
5. Install the code
    
    ``cd cloudmesh-katukota``
    
    ``python setup.py install``
    
    ``pip install .``